    "headline": "Meta (META) Builds Its First India AI Data Center With Reliance",
    "summary": "Meta Platforms (NasdaqGS:META) is partnering with Reliance Industries to build a large-scale AI-enabled data center in India. The facility is Meta’s first built-to-suit data center in the region and is planned to run on renewable energy. The project will use desalinated seawater for cooling and is expected to support Meta’s global AI compute needs. This collaboration aligns with India’s push to position itself as an AI and data center hub. Meta Platforms is deepening its physical footprint...",
